```mermaid graph TD;
    A[Encounter a Problem] --> B{Is this an access issue?};
    
    B -- Yes --> C[Find alternative method: API workaround, manual export, third-party tool];
    C --> D[Test alternative methods];
    D --> E{Did the alternative method work?};
    
    E -- Yes --> F[Document solution and proceed];
    E -- No --> G[Try a second alternative solution];
    G --> E;

    B -- No --> H{Have I researched a solution?};
    
    H -- No --> I[Use GPT-4, YouTube, Documentation, or Forums];
    I --> H;

    H -- Yes --> J{Have I tested at least two possible solutions?};
    
    J -- No --> K[Test multiple approaches before escalating];
    K --> J;

    J -- Yes --> L{Is external access or admin approval needed?};
    
    L -- Yes --> M[Request necessary access/approval];
    M --> N[Wait for response, then retry alternative solutions];
    N --> J;
    
    L -- No --> O[Document failed attempts and escalate to manager];
    O --> P[Submit a detailed report with problem, solutions tried, and what is needed];
    P --> Q[Manager reviews and provides direction];
```
